column1: #dig start(16; 12; Center tile of a 31x23 rectangle) This is a 31x23 layout of an apartment level; the design "cribbed from the wiki" by Meeker. I count 26 apartments
column5: one could easily dig out a bit more to make N/S/E/W 3-tile-wide corridors. And the 3x3 solid center leaves room to build taodih's 3x3 counter-clockwise spiral ramp staircase.
